{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> \u2757\ufe0f PLEASE NOTE \u2757\ufe0f </h2>Bladequest started out as a prototype for my upcoming sandbox action rpg Raidborn and has been transformed into a small highscore-based game, also including a short story mode. I brought it to steam, to get familiar with the platform and be prepared for Raidborn and to offer you a way to support Phodex Games. Find out more about Raidborn on YouTube, where I do weekly devlogs.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897700/extras/Quotes_GIF.gif?t=1656146421\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897700/extras/XMAS_Update_Features.gif?t=1656146421\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> \u26a1\ufe0f THE ULTIMATE DUNGEON \u26a1\ufe0f </h2>Are you ready to explore an infinite dungeon, filled with enemies, weapons and loot? Then jump right into the all-new endless mode!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897700/extras/Room_GIF.gif?t=1656146421\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> \ud83d\udc51 BECOME THE LOOTER KING \ud83d\udc51</h2><br>Fight through the endless dungeon, loot all you can, compete with the world's best, and become the &quot;Looter King&quot;!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> \u2694\ufe0f FIGHT THE UNDEAD \u2694\ufe0f</h2><br>The fully-fledged first person combat system allows you to send the undead back to hell using one-handed weapons, shields, two-handed weapons and bows!<br><br>Find better equipment in every boss room, gear up and dominate your opponents!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> \u2728FEEL THE ATMOSPHERE \u2728</h2><br>The soundscape, the lightning ambience, the charming Polygon-Look and the detailed levels ensure a deep and unique atmosphere!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udd2e FIND A CURE \ud83d\udd2e</h2><br>Play in story mode and help your brave companion, Veronica, find a cure for her brother, who has been struck by a terrible disease. Explore a sinister castle ruin, infested by the undead, and face the dark Shadowlord.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> \ud83d\udcaa\ud83c\udffb SUPPORT THE DEVELOPMENT OF TRUE INDIE GAMES \ud83d\udcaa\ud83c\udffb</h2><br>By purchasing you boost the development of larger-scaled games of this type and give me the opportunity to increase the quality of the game, create more content, hire people, build a business and bring sustainable improvements to the gaming industry.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> \u27a1\ufe0f FEATURES WAITING FOR YOU \u2b05\ufe0f</h2><br><br>\u2714\ufe0f Explore an infinite dungeon in the new &quot;Endless Mode&quot;<br><br>\u2714\ufe0f Compete with players all over the world<br><br>\u2714\ufe0f Charming Polygon-Look<br><br>\u2714\ufe0f Carefully handcrafted dungeon rooms<br><br>\u2714\ufe0f Story mode<br><br>\u2714\ufe0f Fight with sword, shield, mace, axe, or bow<br><br>\u2714\ufe0f Different color schemes<br><br>\u2714\ufe0f Highly atmospheric game experience<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897700/extras/About_Me_Graphic.png.jpg?t=1656146421\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Saviour","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/897700/8ec64d25379b43dfc2bbee0d4c5c5ea9941e7d36.jpg"},{"name":"Looterking","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/897700/6e0621dca58f4c9565d63981e0fc7462324b5fdf.jpg"},{"name":"Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/897700/6914e7e9da1cc04e179cef72daf21b0aa3904ac3.jpg"},{"name":"Adventurer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/897700/b979294fa899d270427d3b7c482f458cdb45b605.jpg"},{"name":"Warrior","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/897700/cf04600bd96f909438baf227a32491028cc23c60.jpg"},{"name":"Champion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.